OL,3,CTeen killed by drug driver was 'smart,
OL,4,Cfunny and and a charmer', says mum
OL,6,FThe mother of a teenager who died when
OL,7,Fhe was knocked off his moped by a drug
OL,8,Fdriver has said he was "a charmer" who
OL,9,Fwanted to live his life to the fullest.
OL,11,FDaniel Davies had recently celebrated
OL,12,Fhis 16th birthday when he died on 17
OL,13,FApril 2022.
OL,15,FHarry Charlton, 29, has been jailed
OL,16,Ffor five years for causing his death
OL,17,Fby careless driving while over the
OL,18,Fprescribed limit of drugs.
