OL,3,CTeen killed by drug driver was 'smart,
OL,4,Cfunny and and a charmer', says mum
OL,6,FThe court heard how he drove through a
OL,7,Fred light at the through-about
OL,8,Fjunction near Warmley and hit Daniel,
OL,9,Fwho was driving his moped.
OL,11,FWhen he was tested, Charlton was found
OL,12,Fto be just over the legal limit for
OL,13,Fcannabis.
OL,15,FDaniel died at the scene after
OL,16,Fsuffering a head injury.
OL,18,FImmediately after the sentencing,
OL,19,FDaniel's mother Samantha said she was
OL,20,F"expecting more" and she felt the
OL,21,Fsentence "wasn't long enough".
