OL,3,CTeen killed by drug driver was 'smart,
OL,4,Cfunny and and a charmer', says mum
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News West Country
OL,7,Fearlier, she Daniel was "very smart"
OL,8,Fand "funny".
OL,10,FShe added: "He used to come home after
OL,11,Fbeing out and he'd go up to his bed
OL,12,Fand I'd lie next to him and we'd chat
OL,13,Ffor ages.
OL,15,F"He had the world, he had everybody
OL,16,Faround his little finger. He was a
OL,17,Fcharmer."
OL,19,FRecounting the events of the night
OL,20,FDaniel died, she said: "I messaged Dan
OL,21,Fto see where he was.
