OL,3,CTeen killed by drug driver was 'smart,
OL,4,Cfunny and and a charmer', says mum
OL,6,F"He wasn't due in til 11 so I wasn't
OL,7,Foverly concerned but he'd only had his
OL,8,Fbike four days so I was obviously a
OL,9,Flittle bit more nervous about him
OL,10,Fbeing out than I would have been and I
OL,11,Fgot no reply.
OL,13,F"Then his girlfriend's dad phoned me
OL,14,Fand said 'there's been an accident.
OL,16,F"We don't know if Dan's involved
OL,17,Fbecause we can't get to the ring road'
OL,18,Fbut his girlfriend Kasha had been
OL,19,Ftracking him on her phone and the
OL,20,Ftracker showed his bike at being on
OL,21,Fthe ring-road."
