OL,3,CTeen killed by drug driver was 'smart,
OL,4,Cfunny and and a charmer', says mum
OL,6,FSamantha rushed to the scene but
OL,7,Fwasn't allowed beyond the police
OL,8,Fcordon.
OL,10,F"The rest of it is a bit of a blur to
OL,11,Fbe honest. Somebody said that somebody
OL,12,Fwould be down to talk to me. I don't
OL,13,Fknow who said that.
OL,15,F"And then two policemen were walking
OL,16,Fdown from the ring-road towards where
OL,17,FI was and I said to them 'Is it Dan?'
OL,18,Fand they said 'Yes' and I said 'Is he
OL,19,Fdead?' and they just said 'Yes.'
