OL,3,CTeen killed by drug driver was 'smart,
OL,4,Cfunny and and a charmer', says mum
OL,6,FSamantha's pain was compounded by the
OL,7,Ffact that she had lost her husband
OL,8,Fjust four months before Daniel's death.
OL,10,FBut she said that, rather than being
OL,11,Fconsumed by grief, the double tragedy
OL,12,Fdrives her to live her life to the
OL,13,Ffullest.
OL,15,FShe said: "I'm living for him. I just
OL,16,Fdo things out of my comfort zone
OL,17,Fbecause I want to do it because I'm
OL,18,Fliving for Dan, I'm living for both of
OL,19,Fthem.
